# endDocument()

**Instance Method**

This method is invoked at the end of the printing session.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor func endDocument()
```

## Discussion

If you override this method, call the superclass implementation.

## Writing Conforming Rendering Instructions

- **beginDocument()**: Invoked at the beginning of the printing session, this method sets up the current graphics context.
- **endPage()**: Writes the end of a conforming page.
